    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, maintained to an exacting standard that defies its pre-owned status. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a level of care synonymous with showroom quality. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a testament to automotive excellence.",
