    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is spotless, the paint is gleaming, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, so if you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
