    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2011 Porsche Cayman R in collector-grade condition. This example features the 3.4L DFI flat-six, delivering 330 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by the R-exclusive 20mm lowered sport suspension and lightweight aluminum body panels. Mechanically flawless, the powertrain is free of leaks and exhibits perfect operational sync, while the exterior retains its original factory finish with consistent paint depth readings throughout. The interior showcases factory carbon fiber bucket seats with zero bolster wear. Meticulously maintained with a fully documented service history, this is a turn-key enthusiast machine for the discerning driver.",
